---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import ButtonLink from "@/components/ButtonLink.astro";
import TimeTable from "@/components/TimeTable.astro";
import MapFrame from "@/components/MapFrame.astro";
import hero from "./_hero.webp?url";

const ja = {
  title: "京葉地区一泊お泊まり会のご案内",
};

const en = {
  title: "Keiyo Area Overnight Retreat Announcement",
};

const timetable1 = {
  caption: "━ 1日目 ━",
  rows: [
    { th: "15:00", td: "受付開始" },
    { th: "16:00", td: "開会式" },
    { th: "17:30", td: "夕食" },
    { th: "19:00", td: "集会" },
    { th: "21:00", td: "交流会" },
    { th: "22:00", td: "自由、入浴" },
    { th: "23:00", td: "交流会" },
    { th: "24:00", td: "就寝" },
  ],
};

const timetable2 = {
  caption: "━ 2日目 ━",
  rows: [
    { th: "6:30", td: "デボーション" },
    { th: "7:00", td: "朝食" },
    { th: "8:30", td: "レクリエーション" },
    { th: "11:00", td: "集会" },
    { th: "13:00", td: "昼食" },
    { th: "14:30", td: "テーマ別集会" },
    { th: "16:30", td: "閉会式" },
    { th: "17:30", td: "解散" },
  ],
};
---

<Layout title={ja.title}>
  <div class="welcome block" style={{ backgroundImage: `url(${hero})` }}>
    <header class="header">
      <h1 class="h1">{ja.title}<br />{en.title}</h1>
    </header>
    <div class="theme">
      <p>みことばによる交わり<br />- 使徒17:11 -</p>
      <p>Fellowship through the Word<br />- Acts 17:11 -</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <main class="main">
    <section class="section">
      <p>
        主の御名を賛美いたします。京葉地区での一泊お泊まり会の開催をご案内申し上げます。
      </p>
      <p>
        この集まりを通じて、信仰の仲間と共に深い交流を持ち、主の愛に満ちた時間を過ごせることを願っています。どうぞご参加ください。主に在りて。
      </p>
      <p>
        Praise be to the name of the Lord. We are pleased to announce the
        holding of an overnight gathering in the Keiyo area.
      </p>
      <p>
        Through this gathering, we hope to have deep fellowship with fellow
        believers and spend a time filled with the Lord's love. Please join us.
        In the Lord.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2 class="head-1">概要<br /><em>Event Overview</em></h2>

      <h3 class="head-2">日時<br /><em>Date and Time</em></h3>
      <p>
        2024年9月22日(日) - 23日(月・祝)<br />
        Sep 22 (Sun) - Sep 23 (Mon, Holiday), 2024
      </p>

      <h3 class="head-2">会場<br /><em>Venue</em></h3>
      <p>
        BumB 東京スポーツ文化館
        <a href="https://www.ys-tokyobay.co.jp/index.html">🔗</a><br />
        BumB Tokyo Sports Culture Center
      </p>

      <h3 class="head-2">講師<br /><em>Speaker</em></h3>
      <p>
        滝山聖書バプテスト教会 高木拓哉伝道師<br />
        Takagi Takuya, Evangelist
        <span class="no-wrap">from Takiyama Bible Baptist Church</span>
      </p>

      <h3 class="head-2">参加費<br /><em>Participation Fee</em></h3>
      <p>
        一般: 8,000円 / 22歳以下: 7,000円<br />
        General: ¥8,000 / Under 22: ¥7,000
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2 class="head-1">プログラム詳細<br /><em>Program Details</em></h2>

      <h3 class="head-2">タイムテーブル<br /><em>Timetable</em></h3>
      <TimeTable {...timetable1} />
      <TimeTable {...timetable2} />

      <h3 class="head-2">テーマ別集会<br /><em>Thematic Meetings</em></h3>
      <p>
        今回は、5つのテーマに分かれた特別な集会を開催いたします。ご興味のあるテーマを選んで、どうぞ自由にご参加ください。各集会でお会いできるのを楽しみにしています！
      </p>
      <p>
        We are excited to offer five special gatherings, each with its own
        unique theme. Feel free to join any gathering that catches your
        interest. We look forward to seeing you at the one you choose!
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2 class="head-1">申し込み<br /><em>Application</em></h2>

      <h3 class="head-2">申し込み方法<br /><em>Application Method</em></h3>
      <p>次のリンクより、Webフォームからお申し込みください。</p>
      <p>Please apply using the web form from the following link.</p>

      <ButtonLink
        href="https://form.nitonabbc.org/#/entry/2024/09"
        target="_blank"
      >
        参加申し込み - Apply Now
      </ButtonLink>

      <h3 class="head-2">申込期限<br /><em>Application Deadline</em></h3>
      <div class="notice">
        <p><strong>2024年8月4日(日)<br />August 4, 2024 (Sunday)</strong></p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2 class="head-1">その他の情報<br /><em>Additional Information</em></h2>

      <h3 class="head-2">持ち物<br /><em>What to Bring</em></h3>

      <h3 class="head-2">アクセス<br /><em>Access</em></h3>
      <MapFrame
        src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d12968.426070133624!2d139.8299139!3d35.6497472!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x6018883c5dbb0623%3A0xc26f94a6ff247d1a!2zQnVtQiDmnbHkuqzjgrnjg53jg7zjg4TmlofljJbppKg!5e0!3m2!1sja!2sjp!4v1718553573811!5m2!1sja!2sjp"
      />

      <h3 class="head-2">駐車場<br /><em>Parking Information</em></h3>

      <h3 class="head-2">お問い合わせ<br /><em>Contact Information</em></h3>
      <p>
        ご質問やご不明な点がございましたら、LINE
        オープンチャットを通じてお気軽にお問い合わせください。以下のリンクからオープンチャットにご参加いただけます。
      </p>
      <p>
        LINE
        オープンチャットは、匿名で参加できるチャットサービスです。誰でも簡単に参加でき、質問や相談がしやすい環境が整っています。どうぞご利用ください。
      </p>
      <p>
        If you have any questions or need further information about the upcoming
        gatherings or any other activities, please feel free to contact us
        through our LINE Open Chat. You can join the Open Chat via the following
        link.
      </p>
      <p>
        LINE Open Chat is a chat service that allows you to participate
        anonymously. It’s easy for anyone to join and provides a convenient way
        to ask questions and share your thoughts. We encourage you to take
        advantage of this service for any inquiries or discussions.
      </p>
      <p><strong>🔐 参加コード：0333</strong></p>

      <ButtonLink
        href="https://line.me/ti/g2/WYr1mnNiAIT7mb_pyn2T5JoEMcZXyGUPchf7IA"
        target="_blank"
      >
        LINE オープンチャット
      </ButtonLink>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<footer class="footer"><small>担当：仁戸名聖書バプテスト教会</small></footer>

<style>
  .welcome {
    background: var(--color-text) no-repeat center center / cover;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .header {
    color: white;
    line-height: 2;
    margin: 10vh auto auto;
    text-shadow:
      0 0 3px #2e8b57,
      0 0 5px #2e8b57,
      0 0 8px #2e8b57;
  }

  .theme {
    background: linear-gradient(to right, #00640080, #556b2f80, #2e8b5780);
    border-radius: 5px;
    color: white;
    font-size: 125%;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin: auto auto 10vh;
    padding: 0 1.5em;
    text-shadow: 0 1px black;
  }

  .h1 {
    font-size: 100%;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .main {
    --color-primary: #2e8b57;
    --color-accent: #cc0074;
    margin: auto;
    max-width: 600px;
    padding: 0 1.5em;
  }

  .section {
    margin: 15vh 0;
  }

  .footer {
    padding: 4em 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  @media (min-width: 1200px) {
    .welcome {
      font-size: 1.5vw;
    }
  }
</style>
